txtRns.text: In accordance with RD Instruction 2006-B, all unnumbered letters and State issuances
must be submitted to the National Office for either prior approval or post approval.
Appendix 10 may serve as a placeholder for unnumbered letters and State issuances if
a paper master manual is retained.
